**Depth 3 with three different unary symbols.**

```elixir
race(
  fn opts ->
    prove(
      ~p"""
      thf(f, type, f: $i>$i).
      thf(g, type, g: $i>$i).
      thf(h, type, h: $i>$i).
      thf(conj, conjecture,
        ![X:$i, Y:$i]: ( (X = Y) => (f @ (g @ (h @ X)) = f @ (g @ (h @ Y))) )
      ).
      """,
      opts
    )
  end,
  configs
)
```

