**Congruence over a binary symbol in both argument positions.**

```elixir
race(
  fn opts ->
    prove(
      ~p"""
      thf(f, type, f: $i>$i>$i).
      thf(conj, conjecture,
        ![X:$i, Y:$i, U:$i, V:$i]:
          ( ((X = Y) & (U = V)) => (f @ X @ U = f @ Y @ V) )
      ).
      """,
      opts
    )
  end,
  configs
)
```

