**Forced clash through congruence.**

```elixir
race(
  fn opts ->
    prove(
      ~p"""
      thf(a, type, a: $i).
      thf(b, type, b: $i).
      thf(f, type, f: $i>$i).
      thf(eq, axiom, a = b).
      thf(hyp, axiom, f @ a != f @ b).
      thf(conj, conjecture, $false).
      """,
      opts
    )
  end,
  configs
)
```

